name: Chocolate Truffle
description: Chocolate cake with slick layers of cream and truffle topped of with a placid layer of chocolate truffle.

name: Red Velvet
description: King of cakes, prepared as a layer cake topped with cooked roux icing.

name: Black Forest
description: Chocolate sponge cake layered with the lightest whipped cream and a glorious topping of chocolate flakes and fine red cherries.

name: White Forest
description: Vanilla cake with a snowy covering of whipped cream. The sides are adorned with white chocolate, topped off with bright red cherries.

name: Irish Coffee
description: Chocolate sponge with smooth layers of Irish coffee cream and chocolate cream, topped off with a clear lake of Irish coffee cream and chocolate cream.

name: Praline Butterscotch
description: White sponge with a delicious filling of butterscotch. Covered in whipped cream and an excess of praline on the sides.

name: Vancho
description: This is vanilla and chocolate sponge, topped off with an eye illuminating layer of white and milk chocolate.

name: Blueberry Cheese Cake
description: Thick creamy filling of cheese over a thinner crust and topped with sweet blueberry reduction
